OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has arrived in Kyiv
OL,7,Ffor his final visit to Ukraine visit
OL,8,Fas prime minister.
OL,10,FHe arrived in the capital on Thursday
OL,11,Fmorning, just hours after overnight
OL,12,Fair strikes killed two people and
OL,13,Finjured five in the city, according to
OL,14,FUkraine's State Emergency Service.
OL,16,FStarmer said the farewell visit would
OL,17,Fshow the UK's "cast-iron" support of
OL,18,FUkraine will "always endure".
