OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784236711
OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FThe PM is expected to tell the
OL,7,FPresident of Ukraine, Volodymyr
OL,8,FZelenskyy, that the UK will continue
OL,9,Fto back his country under Andy
OL,10,FBurnham's leadership.
OL,12,FZelenskyy could also be facing a test
OL,13,Fof his political authority.
OL,15,FHundreds of protesters gathered in
OL,16,Fdowntown Kyiv on Thursday as Zelenskyy
OL,17,Fmoved to dismiss his popular defence
OL,18,Fminister, as parliament appointed a
OL,19,Fnew prime minister as part of a major
OL,20,Fgovernment reshuffle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
