OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FOutgoing Defence Minister Mykhailo
OL,7,FFedorov, 35, is considered to be a
OL,8,Fmoderniser whose technological
OL,9,Fexpertise is credited in part with a
OL,10,Fsignificant improvement in Ukraine's
OL,11,Fmilitary performance in recent months
OL,12,Fagainst Russia's bigger army.
OL,14,FZelenskyy did not publicly give a
OL,15,Freason for Fedorov's anticipated exit,
OL,16,Fbut unconfirmed reports said that the
OL,17,Fdefence minister had a strained
OL,18,Frelationship with General Oleksandr
OL,19,FSyrskyi, the commander of Ukraine's
OL,20,Farmed forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
