OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FAhead of his visit, Starmer said:
OL,7,F"When I became Prime Minister, I knew
OL,8,Fthe UK must not simply stand with
OL,9,FUkraine in the moment, but help build
OL,10,Fthe foundations of its long-term
OL,11,Fsecurity and success.
OL,13,F"That's why we put the UK at the
OL,14,Fcentre of a stronger Europe `
OL,15,Finvesting more money into defence,
OL,16,Fleading the way in the war fighting
OL,17,Ftechnologies of the future and doing
OL,18,Feverything we can to put Ukraine in
OL,19,Fthe strongest possible position."
