OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FStarmer will also hear how allies can
OL,7,Fsupport Ukraine.
OL,9,FA #61 million contract with BAE
OL,10,FSystems means 150 British-made,
OL,11,Fartillery gun barrels will be given to
OL,12,Fthe country to strengthen their
OL,13,Fdefence against Russia.
OL,15,FMade in Sheffield, this is the first
OL,16,Ftime forged artillery barrels have
OL,17,Fbeen produced in the UK for nearly two
OL,18,Fdecades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
