OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FUkraine continues to face bombardment
OL,7,Ffrom Russia as strikes hit the capital
OL,8,Fon Wednesday night, killing two and
OL,9,Finjuring five.
OL,11,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,12,FZelenskyy confirmed the death toll in
OL,13,Fa post on X:
OL,15,FPosting on Telegram, the city's mayor
OL,16,FVitali Klitschko said one of those
OL,17,Finjured was a teenager.
OL,19,FUkraine's State Emergency Service said
OL,20,F27 rescue vehicles and 150 rescue
OL,21,Fworkers attended the site,
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
