OL,3,CStarmer visits Ukraine to show 'cast
OL,4,Ciron' support in final days as PM
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe PM is spending his final days in
OL,12,Foffice highlighting what he sees as
OL,13,Fhis legacy, including support for
OL,14,FUkraine.
OL,16,FIn his time in office he signed a 100-
OL,17,Fyear partnership between the UK and
OL,18,FUkraine, to promote defence and trade
OL,19,Fties with the country.
